<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>PMcore - Otimize seus processos</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        /* Estilos específicos da Landing Page para manter organizado */
        .hero {
            background-color: var(--pm-dark);
            color: var(--pm-white);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
        }
        .hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        
        .pricing-section {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 2rem;
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .plan-card {
            background: var(--pm-white);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 2rem;
            width: 30%;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border: 2px solid transparent;
        }
        
        .plan-card:hover { border-color: var(--pm-blue); }
        .plan-card h3 { color: var(--pm-navy); font-size: 1.5rem; }
        .plan-price { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: bold; margin: 1rem 0; color: var(--pm-dark); }
        
        .btn-primary {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: var(--pm-blue);
            color: var(--pm-white);
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover { background-color: var(--pm-blue-hover); }
        
        .nav-login {
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            color: var(--pm-white);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            border: 1px solid var(--pm-white);
            padding: 8px 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header class="hero">
        <a href="/login" class="nav-login">Já tenho conta (Login)</a>
        <h1>Bem-vindo ao PMcore</h1>
        <p>A plataforma definitiva de CRM e gestão para o seu negócio.</p>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="pricing-section">
            <div class="plan-card">
                <h3>Básico</h3>
                <p>Ideal para autônomos</p>
                <div class="plan-price">R$ 49/mês</div>
                <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <li>✓ 1 Usuário</li>
                    <li>✓ CRM Básico</li>
                    <li>✓ Suporte por Email</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/checkout/basico" class="btn-primary">Assinar Básico</a>
            </div>

            <div class="plan-card" style="border-color: var(--pm-blue); transform: scale(1.05);">
                <h3>Pro</h3>
                <p>Para pequenas equipes</p>
                <div class="plan-price">R$ 99/mês</div>
                <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <li>✓ Até 5 Usuários</li>
                    <li>✓ CRM Completo</li>
                    <li>✓ Dashboard Avançado</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/checkout/pro" class="btn-primary">Assinar Pro</a>
            </div>

            <div class="plan-card">
                <h3>Enterprise</h3>
                <p>Empresas consolidadas</p>
                <div class="plan-price">R$ 299/mês</div>
                <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <li>✓ Usuários Ilimitados</li>
                    <li>✓ API Customizada</li>
                    <li>✓ Suporte 24/7</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/checkout/enterprise" class="btn-primary">Assinar Enterprise</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

</body>
</html>